        All data analyses were performed using the statistical
        software package <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">SAS</ENAMEX> (<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">SAS Institute</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Cary</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">NC</ENAMEX>). Height
        comparisons between <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">genotypes</ENAMEX> were made based on linear
        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">regression</ENAMEX>. Basic statistics on the flowering time
